rt tells the stories of children living in appalling conditions who suffer from various forms of trauma and rejection. The book also includes a number of case studies that demonstrate the need for and effectiveness of the theory. Julien shows that such children, if given a chance, can not only become healthy but find new meaning in life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aMEDICAL / Pediatrics.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077357229440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773572294423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773572294/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles